---

<section class="hero">
  <div class="left">
  <img class="pattern" src="/img/Pattern.png" alt="MÃ¸nster">
  <div class="hero-content">
  <h2>Empowering Your <br> Business Growth</h2>
  <p>Discover tailored strategies and expert insights to take your business to the next level. Let us help you navigate challenges and achieve sustainable success.</p>
  <button type="submit">Book a Meeting</button>
 </div>
